{"tid":1547820,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"致各位示威者","createTime":"2019-09-06T20:19:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T20:29:34.000Z","uid":53055,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d1d91ee2aaa463e808e52707705e446d9910f73f","tid":1547820,"uid":53055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T20:19:10.000Z","msg":"你地只係一班無腦既垃圾，其他人講咩你地就信咩，點解班UC講野你地會信，人地改左玩法，鏡頭前唔會打你，等捉到入自己地方就到仆街，UC都唔會佩帶證明身份既物品，返到去有專人分別是否誘餌，任何人都唔好盡信，諗下對局世影響或者能否當日獲得最佳戰果。<br />\n<br />\n現在係素人指路唔係冷氣軍師教路，分析本日四路：太子，沙田，青衣，遮打。<br />\n遮打：左膠集會，用愛救港。<br />\n青衣：陷阱，好心做壞事。<br />\n沙田：私人派對，對方最脆弱時刻<br />\n太子：乞求聚會，求敵人施捨<br />\n<br />\n諗清楚你地想做咩事，目的係咩，用咩方法可以達成目的。"},{"pid":"e422bb6e3f230218dbeff55f69bef74c89a763a6","tid":1547820,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T20:19:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0fe4bf81176958d0b7998803963d53ccb6157d5a","tid":1547820,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T20:19:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一句講晒，睇哩個post</span></span><br />\n[置頂/請廣傳/多圖] 907 遊客LOOK 暢遊大嶼山指南<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547426</a>"},{"pid":"e9eb8ae0f25dd15f76b5a8f0ac323f838abc3f0d","tid":1547820,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fe4bf81176958d0b7998803963d53ccb6157d5a","tid":1547820,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T20:19:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一句講晒，睇哩個post</span></span><br />\n[置頂/請廣傳/多圖] 907 遊客LOOK 暢遊大嶼山指南<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547426</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T20:29:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dL2K1YC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdL2K1YC.jpg&h=145171af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足們:<br />\n我整